      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　あそこにいるのってサニピの子じゃん",
      "startTime": 40.0730376561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "（わっ！　こっち見た……！　目線は嬉しいけど）\n（ど、どどど、ど、どうしよう……）",
      "startTime": 48.7666637421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃ～ん、昨日のドラマ観た？\n今、kanaさんと話してたんだけど",
      "startTime": 55.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
